David Phetoe Johannesburg — The funeral details for veteran actor David Phetoe has been confirmed. Speaking to The Juice family spokesperson Molefe Pheto says the funeral of David Phetoe (picture below) will take place at the St Mary’s Cathedral in Johannesburg tomorrow. A memorial for the star was held on Wednesday at the SABC studios in Auckland Park, Johannesburg. Molefe says the funeral service will be open to the public. “He was a person of the people so there is no way we can make it private.” News of David’s death surfaced on Friday 2 February. The star was 85. — News24.